---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Service — UniversityX"
  description="Read the terms and conditions governing use of the UniversityX platform."
>
  <div class="bg-[#FBF8F1]">
    <Navbar />
  </div>

  <main class="bg-[#FBF8F1] min-h-screen">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">

      <h1 class="font-['Playfair_Display'] text-4xl font-bold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-[#1A0533]/50 mb-12">Last updated: May 5, 2026</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none text-[#1A0533]/80 space-y-10">

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
          <p>
            By accessing or using UniversityX at
            <a href="https://universityx.app" class="text-[#BB39B4] underline underline-offset-2">https://universityx.app</a>
            (the "Platform"), you agree to be bound by these Terms of Service ("Terms"). If you do not agree to these Terms, please do not use the Platform.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            These Terms apply to all visitors, learners, instructors, and any other users of the Platform.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">2. About UniversityX</h2>
          <p>
            UniversityX is an online learning platform that connects learners with instructors for courses, workshops, and community programmes focused on in-demand skills. We facilitate learning experiences — we are not responsible for the content or outcomes of individual courses unless explicitly stated.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">3. Accounts & Registration</h2>
          <p>To access certain features, you may need to create an account. You agree to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>Provide accurate, current, and complete information during registration</li>
            <li>Maintain the security of your account credentials</li>
            <li>Notify us immediately at <a href="mailto:hello@universityx.app" class="text-[#BB39B4] underline underline-offset-2">hello@universityx.app</a> or <a href="mailto:officialuniversityx@gmail.com" class="text-[#BB39B4] underline underline-offset-2">officialuniversityx@gmail.com</a> of any unauthorised use of your account</li>
            <li>Take responsibility for all activity that occurs under your account</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">
            You must be at least 13 years old to create an account. By creating an account, you confirm that you meet this requirement.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">4. Courses & Workshops</h2>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mt-4 mb-2">For Learners</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
            <li>Access to courses is granted upon successful enrolment (paid or free as specified).</li>
            <li>Course content is for your personal, non-commercial use only.</li>
            <li>You may not share, resell, or reproduce course materials without written permission.</li>
            <li>Completion certificates, where issued, are provided for personal use and do not constitute formal academic credentials unless explicitly stated.</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mt-5 mb-2">For Instructors</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1">
            <li>By submitting course content, you grant UniversityX a non-exclusive licence to host, display, and distribute your materials on the Platform.</li>
            <li>You are responsible for ensuring your content does not infringe on any third-party intellectual property rights.</li>
            <li>You must accurately represent your qualifications and the outcomes learners can expect.</li>
            <li>UniversityX reserves the right to remove content that violates these Terms or our quality standards.</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">5. Payments & Refunds</h2>
          <p>
            Where courses or workshops require payment, pricing will be displayed clearly before purchase. All fees are charged in the currency shown at checkout.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Refund eligibility varies by programme. Where a refund policy applies, it will be stated on the specific course or workshop page. If you believe you are entitled to a refund, contact us at
            <a href="mailto:hello@universityx.app" class="text-[#BB39B4] underline underline-offset-2">hello@universityx.app</a>
            or <a href="mailto:officialuniversityx@gmail.com" class="text-[#BB39B4] underline underline-offset-2">officialuniversityx@gmail.com</a>
            within 14 days of purchase.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">6. Acceptable Use</h2>
          <p>You agree not to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>Use the Platform for any unlawful or fraudulent purpose</li>
            <li>Harass, abuse, or harm other users or instructors</li>
            <li>Post or share content that is offensive, discriminatory, or misleading</li>
            <li>Attempt to gain unauthorised access to any part of the Platform or its systems</li>
            <li>Scrape, copy, or reproduce Platform content without permission</li>
            <li>Use the Platform to distribute spam or unsolicited communications</li>
            <li>Impersonate any person or organisation</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Violation of these rules may result in suspension or permanent removal of your account without notice.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">7. Intellectual Property</h2>
          <p>
            All content on the Platform created by UniversityX — including but not limited to text, graphics, logos, and the site design — is the property of UniversityX and is protected by applicable intellectual property laws.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Course content created by instructors remains the intellectual property of those instructors, subject to the licence granted to UniversityX under these Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">8. Third-Party Links & Services</h2>
          <p>
            The Platform may contain links to third-party websites or services (e.g. WhatsApp community groups, social media). These are provided for convenience only. UniversityX is not responsible for the content, privacy practices, or availability of any third-party sites.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">9. Disclaimers</h2>
          <p>
            The Platform and its content are provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis without warranties of any kind, either express or implied. UniversityX does not guarantee:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>That the Platform will be uninterrupted, error-free, or secure</li>
            <li>That any specific learning outcomes or career results will be achieved</li>
            <li>The accuracy or completeness of any course content</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">10. Limitation of Liability</h2>
          <p>
            To the fullest extent permitted by law, UniversityX shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the Platform — including loss of earnings, data, or opportunity — even if we have been advised of the possibility of such damages.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            Our total liability to you for any claim arising from use of the Platform shall not exceed the amount you paid us in the 3 months preceding the claim (or $50 USD if you have not made any payment).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">11. Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Your use of the Platform is also governed by our
            <a href="/privacy-policy" class="text-[#BB39B4] underline underline-offset-2">Privacy Policy</a>,
            which is incorporated into these Terms by reference.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">12. Modifications to Terms</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to modify these Terms at any time. We will indicate the date of the most recent update at the top of this page. Continued use of the Platform after any changes constitutes your acceptance of the revised Terms.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">13. Termination</h2>
          <p>
            We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your access to the Platform at our discretion, with or without notice, if we believe you have violated these Terms or for any other legitimate reason. You may also close your account at any time by contacting us.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">14. Governing Law</h2>
          <p>
            These Terms shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of Nigeria. Any disputes arising from these Terms or your use of the Platform shall be subject to the exclusive jurisdiction of the courts of Nigeria.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#1A0533] mb-3">15. Contact Us</h2>
          <p>
            If you have any questions about these Terms, please contact us:
          </p>
          <address class="not-italic mt-2 text-[#1A0533]/80 space-y-1">
            <p><strong>UniversityX</strong></p>
            <p>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@universityx.app" class="text-[#BB39B4] underline underline-offset-2">hello@universityx.app</a> / <a href="mailto:officialuniversityx@gmail.com" class="text-[#BB39B4] underline underline-offset-2">officialuniversityx@gmail.com</a></p>
            <p>Website: <a href="https://universityx.app" class="text-[#BB39B4] underline underline-offset-2">https://universityx.app</a></p>
          </address>
        </section>

      </div>
    </div>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
